definitions.definition: ( kayaking , rafting ) A “jump” over hydraulic backwash in a high- gradient mountain river, an action analogous to a skier jumping a cliff.

main_definition: ( kayaking , rafting ) A “jump” over hydraulic backwash in a high- gradient mountain river, an action analogous to a skier jumping a cliff.
